# LifeFind needs NO API keys, NO credits, NO accounts to run. There is nothing you
# MUST fill in. Everything below is optional.
#
#   LIFELINE_OFFLINE=1   force the bundled offline demo set for every channel
#                        (guaranteed-safe stage demo / CI; default is live sources)
#
# Leave unset for normal operation — LifeFind hits real public sources directly
# and falls back to the offline set automatically if any source is unreachable.
#
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTIONAL: LLM narration. The deterministic engine decides everything (zones,
# scores, the assessment) with or without this. If you set a Groq key, the
# commander's *chat replies* get rephrased into clearer prose — it never changes
# a number or a decision, redacts the subject's identity before any call, and
# falls back to the deterministic text if the key is missing or Groq is down.
#
#   GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...                    # enables narration; unset = fully keyless
#   GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile      # any Groq chat model
#   LIFELINE_NARRATE=0                       # force narration off even with a key set
#
# NEVER commit a real key. Keep it in your local .env (gitignored), not here.
